<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 06:19:59 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>联合国表示，阿富汗鸦片种植在禁令两年后出现反弹并发生变化</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/afghan-opium-cultivation-bounces-shifts-two-years-after-ban-un-says-2024-11-06/</link><description>联合国周三发布的一份报告称，阿富汗长期以来是全球海洛因原材料的主要供应国，自塔利班禁止鸦片罂粟以来，该国的罂粟产量在第二年增加了五分之一，但仍仅是禁令前水平的一小部分。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 05:35:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/afghan-opium-cultivation-bounces-shifts-two-years-after-ban-un-says-2024-11-06/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：“特朗普交易”如火如荼</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-11-06/</link><description>韦恩·科尔 (Wayne Cole) 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 05:33:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-11-06/</guid></item><item><title>台英举行新一轮贸易谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/taiwan-britain-hold-new-round-trade-talks-2024-11-06/</link><description>官员周三表示，台湾和英国将于本周举行新一轮贸易谈判，重点讨论投资和绿色能源。此前，台北希望去年达成一项协议，以促进这家科技巨头的全球参与。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 05:16:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/taiwan-britain-hold-new-round-trade-talks-2024-11-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国国家机密泄露导致前雇员罕见被判死刑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-state-secrets-leak-prompts-rare-death-sentence-ex-employee-2024-11-06/</link><description>中国国家安全部周三表示，一名为中国国家机构工作的前雇员因泄露“国家机密”而被罕见地判处死刑，此前他被指控将自己的 USB 驱动器交给外国间谍机构。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 05:02:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-state-secrets-leak-prompts-rare-death-sentence-ex-employee-2024-11-06/</guid></item><item><title>由于天气好转和折扣，中国十月份出口增长可能加快</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-export-growth-likely-picked-up-speed-oct-better-weather-discounts-2024-11-06/</link><description>尽管制造商和其他主要出口商报告全球需求下降，但受天气好转和大幅折扣的推动，中国 10 月份的出口量可能会以更快的速度增长。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 04:50:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-export-growth-likely-picked-up-speed-oct-better-weather-discounts-2024-11-06/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚情报局长表示，俄罗斯和中国的“新兴轴心”令人不安</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-china-emerging-axis-troubling-says-australia-intelligence-chief-2024-11-06/</link><description>澳大利亚国家情报办公室负责人表示，包括中国、伊朗和朝鲜在内的向俄罗斯提供支持的国家“新兴轴心”是“令人深感不安的战略发展”，西方国家正在努力追赶。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 01:24:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-china-emerging-axis-troubling-says-australia-intelligence-chief-2024-11-06/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示，由于对中国和通胀的担忧，日本制造商11月信心下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/japan-manufacturers-less-confident-november-worries-over-china-inflation-2024-11-05/</link><description>路透社周三的月度调查显示，日本制造商对 11 月份商业状况的信心低于 10 月份，原因是中国经济放缓和持续高通胀率削弱了市场情绪。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 23:12:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/japan-manufacturers-less-confident-november-worries-over-china-inflation-2024-11-05/</guid></item><item><title>随着美国总统竞选结束，从台湾到贸易，中国准备迎接更多竞争</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/taiwan-trade-china-braces-more-rivalry-close-us-presidential-race-ends-2024-11-05/</link><description>随着美国人在数十年来最激烈的总统选举之一中进行投票，中国做好了准备，无论谁获胜，都将导致超级大国在贸易、技术和安全问题上的激烈竞争再持续四年。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 17:09:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/taiwan-trade-china-braces-more-rivalry-close-us-presidential-race-ends-2024-11-05/</guid></item><item><title>阿斯利康股价因潜在的中国调查影响而下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/astrazeneca-shares-fall-report-potential-china-probe-fallout-2024-11-05/</link><description>阿斯利康股价周二录得自 2020 年 3 月以来最糟糕的一天，此前有报道称，该制药商在中国的数十名高管可能卷入中国制药行业多年来最大的保险欺诈案。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 16:09:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/astrazeneca-shares-fall-report-potential-china-probe-fallout-2024-11-05/</guid></item><item><title>共和党议员称美国需要打击中国芯片制造商中芯国际</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-needs-crack-down-chinese-chipmaker-smic-republican-lawmaker-says-2024-11-05/</link><description>一位共和党高级议员指责拜登政府没有采取足够措施阻止中国半导体制造国际公司（中芯国际）加强该国的芯片制造行业和军工联合体。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 15:03:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-needs-crack-down-chinese-chipmaker-smic-republican-lawmaker-says-2024-11-05/</guid></item><item><title>文件显示，中国希望在COP29气候峰会上就贸易措施进行谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-wants-talks-trade-measures-cop29-climate-summit-document-shows-2024-11-05/</link><description>路透社看到的一份文件显示，中国已要求各国在下周举行的 COP29 联合国气候峰会上就碳边境税和其他“限制性贸易措施”举行会谈，北京称这些措施正在伤害发展中国家。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 13:59:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-wants-talks-trade-measures-cop29-climate-summit-document-shows-2024-11-05/</guid></item><item><title>小米投诉后印度召回 Flipkart 反垄断调查报告</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-recalls-flipkart-antitrust-probe-report-after-xiaomi-complaint-2024-11-05/</link><description>一份文件显示，印度反垄断机构已召回其对电子商务巨头沃尔玛旗下 Flipkart 违反竞争法的调查报告，这是继 8 月份针对苹果的报告被撤销后的第二次此类举措。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 13:55:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-recalls-flipkart-antitrust-probe-report-after-xiaomi-complaint-2024-11-05/</guid></item><item><title>Shein 和 Temu 为 2026 年英国版权和竞争索赔审判做好准备</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/shein-temu-gear-up-2026-uk-trial-over-copyright-competition-claims-2024-11-05/</link><description>在线快时尚平台 Shein 和 Temu 正准备于 2026 年在伦敦高等法院接受审判，竞争对手在相互竞争的诉讼中相互指控侵犯版权和反竞争行为。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 12:10:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/shein-temu-gear-up-2026-uk-trial-over-copyright-competition-claims-2024-11-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国媒体报道，中石化天然气公司前高管因受贿被判入狱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/former-sinopec-gas-executive-gets-jail-time-taking-bribes-chinese-media-reports-2024-11-05/</link><description>据中国半官方通讯社中新社周二报道，中国石化一名前高管因受贿被判处 14 年有期徒刑。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 08:47:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/former-sinopec-gas-executive-gets-jail-time-taking-bribes-chinese-media-reports-2024-11-05/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾部长称北约式东南亚安全组织不可行</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/nato-type-southeast-asian-security-group-not-feasible-philippines-minister-says-2024-11-05/</link><description>菲律宾国防部长周二表示，鉴于该地区的利益和联盟存在分歧，目前不可能在东南亚建立类似于北大西洋公约组织（北约）的安全组织。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 08:45:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/nato-type-southeast-asian-security-group-not-feasible-philippines-minister-says-2024-11-05/</guid></item></channel></rss>